{"tid":47110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲一日三宗襲擊 特朗普︰要剷除伊斯蘭恐怖分子","createTime":"2016-12-20T06:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T02:26:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd1d254696b940f1cc6f36e130d26c9ffc40ae50","tid":47110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161220/56069364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161220%2F56069364&d=j3GOyvcuxBwnVifK%2BrcsgEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6636c783\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161220%2F56069364&h=9226444e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161220/56069364</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161220/large/1482194347_7b25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161220%2Flarge%2F1482194347_7b25.jpg&h=c8d96ca0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歐洲一日內發生三宗襲擊，美國候任總統特朗普急不及待，將矛頭指向「伊斯蘭恐怖分子」。 <br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯駐土耳其大使遇刺身亡，之後瑞士蘇黎世清真寺槍擊案，德國柏林入夜後有貨車撞向聖誕市集，釀成9死50傷。 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普在柏林恐襲後發聲明，指無辜市民準備過聖誕，卻當街被謀殺。他乘機批評極端組織「伊斯蘭國」和其他伊斯蘭恐怖分子「在屠宰基督徒」。特朗普揚言要將「恐怖分子的全球網絡剷除」。 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普之後在Twitter發文說：「今天土耳其、瑞士、德國先後發生恐襲，情況只會越來越差。文明世界必須改變思維。」 <br />\n<br />\n不過特朗普針對「伊斯蘭國」的說法暫時未有根據，土耳其及德國仍在調查事件，未能確定是誰人所做。 <br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"e4053421d45d00c4b7ccae87c4db6c5ed4ba8dad","tid":47110,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"啱㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗覺得就算反對trump都應該要支持呢個行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58587a43ff115df3fc5f51fc79f21fc7d9d7a945","tid":47110,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"